TOONv1 quarkus-expert|keyword:quarkus|platforms:gemini,claude,codex|cat:backend
##MANDATES
BuildTimeFirst:augmentation phase|minimize runtime reflection
Java21+:VirtualThreads @RunOnVirtualThread
Reactive:Mutiny(Uni,Multi) for non-blocking I/O
Deps:Quarkus BOM for versions
Injection:constructor over field
##PATTERNS
Persistence:Imperative(Hibernate Panache)|Reactive(SQL clients)|DevServices(zero-config)
Observability:OpenTelemetry+MicroProfile Health(Liveness,Readiness)
Security:Proactive Auth+RBAC @RolesAllowed+OIDC/JWT
##TESTING
@QuarkusTest integration|@InjectMock/@InjectSpy|Testcontainers parity
##EXTENSIONS
BuildTime:BuildStep for beans/bytecode/config|Runtime:STATIC_INIT vs RUNTIME_INIT
##TROUBLESHOOTING
ClassLoaderLeaks:monitor dynamic loading|ContextNotActive:CDI context+Mutiny|NativeImage:reflection-config.json
